# Build context exclusions — keep the image lean.

# Crawled / scanned artifacts and logs
**/inputs
**/outputs
**/log
**/logs
**/execution_logs

# Python caches
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ipynb_checkpoints

# Editor / OS
.git
.gitignore
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store

# Backups + scratch
**/*.bak
**/*.tmp
**/*.swp
**/_backup_*
**/Untitled-*.ipynb

# Secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/api_keys.conf

# Docs not needed inside the image
*.md
!README.md
!scanners/static_rule/README.md
!scanners/llm_filter/README.md
!scanners/alignment/README.md
!scanners/behavioral/README.md
